1
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:42,440
Ji.

2
00:01:02,840 --> 00:01:05,300
Generations have tortured women like this.

3
00:01:05,440 --> 00:01:06,900
If this isn't made public,

4
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:09,060
it would be absolutely intolerable.

5
00:01:09,080 --> 00:01:10,539
What's more terrifying is

6
00:01:10,600 --> 00:01:12,060
that besides those women,

7
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:14,140
there are many infant skeletons,

8
00:01:14,320 --> 00:01:16,120
and they are clearly baby girls.

9
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:17,060
In other words,

10
00:01:17,600 --> 00:01:19,840
because they couldn't produce male heirs,

11
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:21,300
they met such a tragic end.

12
00:01:26,039 --> 00:01:27,000
I finally know why

13
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:29,460
you've liked those things since childhood.

14
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:31,610
You just wanted to see your mother.

15
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:34,640
I was destined never to see my mother one last time.

16
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:41,039
If the pawned wives were mummified

17
00:01:41,039 --> 00:01:42,039
and kept here,

18
00:01:42,240 --> 00:01:44,600
yet your mother's body is the only one missing,

19
00:01:44,600 --> 00:01:45,160
Then...

20
00:01:45,240 --> 00:01:46,200
That means...

21
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:55,000
It's my mother.

22
00:01:55,600 --> 00:01:57,729
Why do you have a portrait of my mother?

23
00:01:57,800 --> 00:01:58,800
Have you seen her?

24
00:01:58,800 --> 00:02:01,200
And you said you couldn't channel spirits.

25
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:05,560
No wonder there were

26
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:07,620
so many dead cats in the Tu residence.

27
00:02:07,720 --> 00:02:09,639
The cats dug holes underground.

28
00:02:09,639 --> 00:02:11,400
To prevent it from being exposed,

29
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:12,120
Master Tu

30
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,900
ordered poison to be put down.

31
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:15,160
So at that time,

32
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:17,200
your mother's remains were exposed

33
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:18,480
and discovered by them.

34
00:02:18,480 --> 00:02:19,280
Then,

35
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:22,960
they were used to fake Lailan's corpse turning into a zombie.

36
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:30,600
Mr. Liu.

37
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:32,040
Thank you

38
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:35,000
for letting me see my mother again.

39
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:49,770
If we hadn't been driven into a corner,

40
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:52,320
we might never have found this place.

41
00:02:52,320 --> 00:02:54,200
So finding no clues up there

42
00:02:54,320 --> 00:02:55,380
is not surprising.

43
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,640
Burn it down!

44
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:59,320
Burn them all!

45
00:03:24,440 --> 00:03:25,600
Stoke the fire!

46
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:27,360
Choke them to death!

47
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:35,760
Grandson.

48
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:37,760
Go back and rest first.

49
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,760
I will stay here

50
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:42,250
and continue to clean up the evil spirits.

51
00:03:49,880 --> 00:03:51,320
As a woman,

52
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:55,160
it is only natural for her to sacrifice herself for the Tu family.

53
00:03:56,160 --> 00:03:58,400
You are the only heir of the Tu family.

54
00:03:58,760 --> 00:04:00,080
Don't be foolish.

55
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:02,400
But remember,

56
00:04:02,880 --> 00:04:05,480
I will only forgive you this once.

57
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:08,800
When we find that girl's body,

58
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,840
I will expose it for three days

59
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,360
to show the world

60
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:14,000
her sins.

61
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:18,160
Only then will the Tu family have peace.

62
00:04:19,200 --> 00:04:20,279
Tell me,

63
00:04:20,640 --> 00:04:21,800
isn't that right?

64
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:25,800
I'm sorry.

65
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:26,800
I object.

66
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:42,440
You brought her back now,

67
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:44,880
hoping I would give you a way out.

68
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:47,440
Isn't it too late?

69
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:50,240
I am giving your Tu family a chance,

70
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:52,400
a chance for everyone in this deep courtyard

71
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:53,480
for all of you

72
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:55,080
to stop being selfish,

73
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:56,450
cold-blooded animals.

74
00:05:05,440 --> 00:05:06,640
What use are you to me?

75
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:08,480
You can't even give birth to a son.

76
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,400
What use

77
00:05:09,520 --> 00:05:10,320
are you

78
00:05:10,320 --> 00:05:11,800
to me?

79
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:12,560
Master, no!

80
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:13,760
What use are you to me!

81
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:14,160
Master!

82
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:15,080
What use are you to me?

83
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:15,600
Master,

84
00:05:15,960 --> 00:05:17,640
Lailan just had a miscarriage.

85
00:05:17,640 --> 00:05:19,640
She can't take this kind of torment.

86
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:22,320
She gave birth to a useless girl anyway.

87
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:24,860
I just had her thrown into the mountains.

88
00:05:25,080 --> 00:05:25,800
This...

89
00:05:26,080 --> 00:05:26,760
This wine,

90
00:05:26,960 --> 00:05:28,360
I'll let you taste it too.

91
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:29,360
Drink it!

92
00:05:29,440 --> 00:05:30,520
Somebody, help!

93
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:31,600
Drink it!

94
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:33,640
No, Father!

95
00:05:38,880 --> 00:05:39,720
Useless!

96
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:41,280
If you weren't such a sickly weakling,

97
00:05:41,280 --> 00:05:44,080
would I have to try every possible way to have a son?

98
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:46,380
If you continue to be so cruel,

99
00:05:46,400 --> 00:05:48,040
don't blame me for disowning you.

100
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:49,040
You beast!

101
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:51,040
How dare you defy me!

102
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:53,760
I'll kill you today!

103
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:54,920
I...

104
00:05:55,640 --> 00:05:56,240
No!

105
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:58,240
Master, please spare my son!

106
00:06:00,400 --> 00:06:00,920
Master!

107
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:01,680
Master!

108
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:02,280
Get lost!

109
00:06:02,440 --> 00:06:02,960
Master!

110
00:06:02,960 --> 00:06:03,560
Get lost!

111
00:06:26,400 --> 00:06:28,680
Murder!

112
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:33,000
Butler!

113
00:06:33,760 --> 00:06:34,560
Butler!

114
00:06:42,200 --> 00:06:43,360
A few days ago,

115
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:45,360
when he ordered the cats to be poisoned,

116
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,600
I found this in the field.

117
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,920
It might come in handy.

118
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:48,960
Okay.

119
00:07:11,200 --> 00:07:13,960
Nonsense.

120
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:15,640
Tell him,

121
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:17,480
he made it all up.

122
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:19,800
It was all Tu Yunmeng's doing.

123
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,440
See?

124
00:07:22,960 --> 00:07:24,600
No one here can believe

125
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:26,560
anything you say.

126
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:29,080
You forced me into the cellar,

127
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:30,920
but I happened to find

128
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:33,840
the secret of the Tu family harming the pawned wives,

129
00:07:33,840 --> 00:07:35,770
and I also found crucial evidence.

130
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:36,960
Unfortunately,

131
00:07:37,159 --> 00:07:38,490
Lailan is already dead.

132
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,080
My ladies.

133
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:42,880
Young Master.

134
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:45,600
Forced by poverty to become a pawned wife,

135
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:48,600
I thought I could go home after giving birth,

136
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:51,280
but who knew the Tu family, due to years of war,

137
00:07:51,520 --> 00:07:52,680
lacked male heirs.

138
00:07:52,840 --> 00:07:54,920
Master Tu also suffered from a hidden illness,

139
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:56,650
beating and scolding me daily.

140
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:58,400
But thanks to the pity of a few,

141
00:07:58,400 --> 00:07:59,930
Lailan felt deeply warmed.

142
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:00,960
However, now,

143
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:03,160
Miss Tu is innocently implicated.

144
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:04,480
Lailan truly cannot bear it,

145
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,680
and can only choose to die,

146
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:07,120
taking on all the sins.

147
00:08:07,200 --> 00:08:08,600
In the next life, I will serve like a beast of burden,

148
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:10,160
and will definitely repay you.

149
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:10,400
Lailan's last words.

150
00:08:10,400 --> 00:08:11,600
Lailan's last words.

151
00:08:18,200 --> 00:08:19,480
Good riddance.

152
00:08:20,400 --> 00:08:22,600
Consider it a life for my son's.

153
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:24,400
Kill this girl too,

154
00:08:24,760 --> 00:08:25,800
and all of this

155
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:27,760
will be completely over.

156
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:29,800
Grandson.

157
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,920
Grandma will teach you now

158
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:34,000
how to manage the Tu family.

159
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:35,280
Remember,

160
00:08:35,760 --> 00:08:37,000
no relationship,

161
00:08:37,159 --> 00:08:38,400
no person,

162
00:08:38,400 --> 00:08:39,880
can be above

163
00:08:40,159 --> 00:08:42,600
the family's interests and honor.

164
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,000
Keep it in mind.

165
00:08:46,760 --> 00:08:47,400
Grandma.

166
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:48,600
Everything,

167
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:50,280
just as Mr. Liu said,

168
00:08:50,560 --> 00:08:52,290
has nothing to do with Yunmeng.

169
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:55,240
Are you confused?

170
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,400
What are you talking about?

171
00:08:56,400 --> 00:08:57,480
Step down!

172
00:08:58,200 --> 00:09:00,530
I have been muddled for over twenty years,

173
00:09:00,800 --> 00:09:02,480
but I am most sober right now.

174
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:03,600
Father

175
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,560
was killed by me.

176
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:07,440
No, Dad!

177
00:09:08,040 --> 00:09:09,280
You sickling,

178
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:11,560
minding your father's business with women!

179
00:09:11,560 --> 00:09:12,520
If you meddle again,

180
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:12,840
I,

181
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:14,560
I'll kill your mother first!

182
00:09:14,880 --> 00:09:15,680
No!

183
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:23,000
No!

184
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:25,200
I smashed the Master to death!

185
00:09:25,800 --> 00:09:27,530
I am willing to die for my crime.

186
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:28,640
My son,

187
00:09:28,880 --> 00:09:30,000
say no more.

188
00:09:30,400 --> 00:09:32,200
Let mother bear all this.

189
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:33,880
What?

190
00:09:36,040 --> 00:09:38,900
He should have suffered this retribution long ago.

191
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:40,000
Then,

192
00:09:40,680 --> 00:09:41,600
if I have a son,

193
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:42,840
can I go home?

194
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:46,480
Get away!

195
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:50,400
Don't you like chanting?

196
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:51,720
Perfect,

197
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:54,880
just chant beside me to add to the fun.

198
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:01,200
How dare you!

199
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:03,660
I married you today just to have a son.

200
00:10:05,280 --> 00:10:06,340
You better behave.

201
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:10,600
Run. Let's see where you can run.

202
00:10:13,160 --> 00:10:14,200
And me.

203
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:16,600
To cover up the truth,

204
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:18,240
I fabricated Lailan's corpse transformation.

205
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:20,300
I should be treated as an accomplice.

206
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,960
Yunmeng is innocent.

207
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:27,800
You,

208
00:10:28,160 --> 00:10:29,760
you're all crazy.

209
00:10:31,680 --> 00:10:32,760
It must be this girl

210
00:10:32,760 --> 00:10:34,440
who bewitched your minds.

211
00:10:34,520 --> 00:10:35,040
Butler,

212
00:10:35,560 --> 00:10:36,640
do it now.

213
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:43,360
Why did you do this?

214
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:45,340
Was everything before

215
00:10:45,760 --> 00:10:47,560
all for nothing?

216
00:10:47,640 --> 00:10:48,880
You know very well

217
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,370
these past two days,

218
00:10:50,640 --> 00:10:52,360
how anxious I've been.

219
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:54,320
Now,

220
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:56,440
I feel completely relieved.

221
00:10:56,680 --> 00:10:57,640
It's just a pity

222
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:59,340
that I implicated you.

223
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:03,400
For you,

224
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:05,160
I am willing

225
00:11:05,400 --> 00:11:06,530
to give everything.

226
00:11:06,560 --> 00:11:07,960
I have no regrets.

227
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:09,480
Since we are going to die,

228
00:11:10,400 --> 00:11:11,840
I will accompany you.

229
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:17,040
Over the years,

230
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:20,420
I've seen with my own eyes how the Master abused others.

231
00:11:21,040 --> 00:11:22,700
I've hated him for a long time.

232
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:29,360
I'll beat you to death!

233
00:11:29,360 --> 00:11:30,620
I'll beat you to death!

234
00:11:30,760 --> 00:11:32,020
I'll beat you to death!

235
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:33,680
You useless thing!

236
00:11:35,960 --> 00:11:37,440
You can't even give birth to a son.

237
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,440
Have you no shame?

238
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,260
I'll beat you to death!

239
00:11:43,760 --> 00:11:46,640
Originally, only that girl had to die.

240
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:49,320
But now, because of you

241
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:51,960
and your so-called search for the truth,

242
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:54,440
so many people have to be dragged into this.

243
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:56,840
Is this the result you wanted?

244
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,600
The truth, for whatever reason,

245
00:11:58,600 --> 00:11:59,480
cannot be tampered with.

246
00:11:59,480 --> 00:12:00,940
This is basic conscience.

247
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:02,360
Besides,

248
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:04,160
they are accomplices

249
00:12:04,240 --> 00:12:05,300
as well as victims.

250
00:12:06,680 --> 00:12:07,920
You think

251
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:10,000
only you can see the truth,

252
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:12,360
and everyone else is beneath you?

253
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:13,840
Old lady, perhaps at first,

254
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:16,200
you also believed the story of the corpse reviving.

255
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:18,000
But you are a perceptive person.

256
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:19,400
Through later observations,

257
00:12:19,400 --> 00:12:21,260
you noticed something was amiss.

258
00:12:21,800 --> 00:12:22,800
Especially after I restored

259
00:12:22,800 --> 00:12:24,480
the appearance of that mummy,

260
00:12:24,600 --> 00:12:27,040
you even guessed the gist of the whole thing.

261
00:12:27,040 --> 00:12:29,800
As the person who knows the Tu family's secrets best,

262
00:12:29,800 --> 00:12:31,480
in order to cover up the fact that generations of the Tu family

263
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:33,000
abused pawned wives,

264
00:12:33,880 --> 00:12:35,800
you chose to play along

265
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,800
and sacrifice Tu Yunmeng alone.

266
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:39,200
Grandma.

267
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:41,040
Is what Liu Chuan said true?

268
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:44,900
You knew everything about what happened in the cellar?

269
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:46,800
How is this possible?

270
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:51,480
You are really smart.

271
00:12:52,600 --> 00:12:54,600
But you should also know that,

272
00:12:55,480 --> 00:12:57,600
for the reputation of the Tu family,

273
00:12:58,200 --> 00:12:59,800
I will do whatever it takes.

274
00:13:00,640 --> 00:13:03,080
By explaining everything,

275
00:13:03,400 --> 00:13:05,400
you are basically asking for death.

276
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:07,240
Aren't you afraid?

277
00:13:07,280 --> 00:13:08,940
Of course I'm afraid of death.

278
00:13:09,040 --> 00:13:11,440
But I'm more afraid of living in ignorance.

279
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:13,760
Very well.

280
00:13:14,400 --> 00:13:16,200
Then I'll send you to hell first.

281
00:13:25,040 --> 00:13:26,200
Okay.

282
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:28,400
Okay.

283
00:13:29,560 --> 00:13:31,560
Since you all want to die,

284
00:13:32,040 --> 00:13:33,880
I will grant your wish.

285
00:13:34,720 --> 00:13:36,240
Go to hell!

286
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:37,000
Grandma.
